    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-02-26T06:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-02-26T06:00:00-05:00" n="675"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d675">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">493.11/1609: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China (<persName corresp="frus1932v03#p_JNT1"
                            type="from">Johnson</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-02-26T19:00:00+08:00"
                            >February 26, 1932—7 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 26—10 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My February 23, 3 p.m.<note n="67" xml:id="d675fn67">Not printed.</note> I have
                    received a letter from <persName corresp="frus1932v03#p_STV1">T. V.
                        Soong</persName> from which I quote the following: <pb facs="0709" n="611"
                        xml:id="pg_611"/>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“I wonder if you have heard anything in the meanwhile from your
                            Government …<note n="68" xml:id="d675fn68">Omission indicated in the
                                original telegram.</note> as payment for this month will be due
                            tomorrow.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1932v03#p_JNT1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
